author: veithen
msg: Removed a couple of redundant test cases. They were comparing the XMLStreamReader returned by getXMLStreamReader and getXMLStreamReaderWithoutCaching with an XMLStreamReader obtained directly from StAX. However, this type of test is implemented in a more sophisticated way by TestGetXMLStreamReader. In particular, TestGetXMLStreamReader not only compares the sequence of event types, but also the return values of various methods of XMLStreamReader for each event.
